WHO   — 'I Don't Want Your Life' — the line · aimed at the father
WHAT  — The spine: the refusal of the vicarious dream, pointed where it actually lands — the dad living through the son.
WHERE — VBL · Varsity Blues (1999)  Framework inputs: Varsity Blues (1999, dir. Brian Robbins, MTV Films/Paramount); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the real engine of West Canaan isn't the coach; it's the fathers, and this line names it.
